  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a pan over medium heat. Add apricot jam, vegetable broth, tapioca flour/water mixture, garlic, and onion to the pan.",
    "Stir until the mixture thickens slightly, about 2-3 minutes.",
    "Add carrots and broccoli florets to the saucepan. Stir occasionally for 5-7 minutes or until vegetables are tender but still crisp.",
    "For noodles, bring water to a boil, add noodles, and cook according to package instructions. Drain well.",
    "Toss cooked noodles into the pan with vegetable mixture, adding salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Sprinkle sesame seeds on top if desired. Serve hot."
  ],
